title: Research
text: I work on problems related to precision poultry nutrition, stochastic feed formulation, and nutrient variability.

title: Research
text:
Current Projects

Stochastic Feed Formulation — integrating nutrient variability into diet models.
Soybean Meal Quality — modeling processing effects on digestibility.
Broiler Breeder Precision Nutrition — evaluating nutritional strategies under heat stress.
Nutrient Variability in Feed Ingredients — quantifying and classifying variability in nutrient profiles.

title: About
text:
About Me
I’m a Ph.D. candidate in Poultry Science & Nutrition, focusing on feed formulation, nutrient modeling, and precision agriculture.

title: Welcome
text:
Hi, I’m Caleb Marshall. I’m currently a Ph.D student at North Carolina State University in the Prestage Department of Poultry Science.
This site is to share some of my research, blog posts, etc.
